    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-07-27T22:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-07-27T22:00:00-05:00" n="566"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d566">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">394.112/16: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Chefoo</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Roberts</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chefoo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-07-28T11:00:00+08:00"
                            >July 28, 1938—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 12:20 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My cipher telegram July 27, 9 p.m. Japanese Consul has called formally: <list>
                        <label>1,</label>
                        <item>to express his regret that Japanese patrols assaulted two
                            Americans.</item>
                        <label>2,</label>
                        <item>to convey information that Japanese commander shall begin punishment
                            of Japanese naval personnel guilty of assault.</item>
                        <label>3,</label>
                        <item>Japanese authorities will take steps to prevent recurrence of
                            incident.</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p>Please telegraph instructions.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Embassy at Hankow and Peiping.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roberts</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
